description:
Our beautiful 3 bedroom apt with 6 real beds is located in beautiful Brooklyn close to shopping transportation and restaurants. Prospect Park, Brooklyn Museum. And the Botanic Garden is just 10 mins away . Sample great tastes of the vibrant Caribbean 
And dance to Carnaval on Labor Day !!

Guests will have access. To a complete kitchen with dishes and Silverware . Cook to you hearts content . 24 hour wi fi  . Blow dryer toaster hot water kettle and micro wave .

I will receive you when you arrive 
And be there to see you off  when you leave and in between I will assist you with all the information you will need to have the best time in NYC !

We are 1 block to the B35 bus and 5 mins to the 2 or 5 train.30 mins toJFK and to lower Manhattan.

We do not provide laundry service
You can wash your clothes at the laundry mat  1.block away. Please keep the Apt Clean.
Thanks . Please recycle all trash.
Checkout is by 11am and checkin is after 3pm
